Package com.platform.audit.internal

Class AuditEvent

java.lang.Object
com.platform.audit.internal.AuditEvent
@Entity public class AuditEvent extends Object
AuditEvent entity for compliance and security audit logging with GDPR support. Uses table partitioning for performance and retention management.
